Prefix          NextHop             Attrs
10.244.1.0/24   fc00:10:99:102::1   [{Origin: i} {AsPath: 65010} {MpReach(ipv4-unicast): {Nexthop: fc00:10:99:102::1, NLRIs: [10.244.1.0/24]}}]
10.244.2.0/24   10.99.102.2         [{Origin: i} {AsPath: 65010} {Nexthop: 10.99.102.2}]
10.244.3.0/24   fc00:10:99:102::2   [{Origin: i} {AsPath: 65010} {MpReach(ipv4-unicast): {Nexthop: fc00:10:99:102::2, NLRIs: [10.244.3.0/24]}}]
10.244.4.0/24   10.99.102.3         [{Origin: i} {AsPath: 65010} {Nexthop: 10.99.102.3}]
10.244.5.0/24   fc00:10:99:102::3   [{Origin: i} {AsPath: 65010} {MpReach(ipv4-unicast): {Nexthop: fc00:10:99:102::3, NLRIs: [10.244.5.0/24]}}]
-- internal-v4-routes.expected --
Prefix          NextHop             Attrs
10.244.1.0/24   10.99.102.1         [{Origin: i} {AsPath: } {Nexthop: 10.99.102.1} {LocalPref: 100}]
10.244.2.0/24   10.99.102.2         [{Origin: i} {AsPath: } {Nexthop: 10.99.102.2} {LocalPref: 100}]
10.244.3.0/24   fc00:10:99:102::2   [{Origin: i} {AsPath: } {LocalPref: 100} {MpReach(ipv4-unicast): {Nexthop: fc00:10:99:102::2, NLRIs: [10.244.3.0/24]}}]
10.244.4.0/24   10.99.102.3         [{Origin: i} {AsPath: } {Nexthop: 10.99.102.3} {LocalPref: 100}]
10.244.5.0/24   fc00:10:99:102::3   [{Origin: i} {AsPath: } {LocalPref: 100} {MpReach(ipv4-unicast): {Nexthop: fc00:10:99:102::3, NLRIs: [10.244.5.0/24]}}]
